---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Kristi Hemmer | Women's Leadership Speaker & Coach"
  description="Meet Kristi Hemmer: educator, entrepreneur, sojourner, storyteller. From 8-year-old dreams to global changemaker, discover her mission to put more women in power."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- SECTION 1: Hero/Introduction -->
    <section class="relative py-20 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink via-moxie-pink-alt to-fierce-flamingo text-white overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/Graphic Elements_Yellow_01.png"
        alt=""
        class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-48 opacity-30"
        aria-hidden="true"
      />

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Meet Kristi</h1>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light mb-6 text-sunny-yellow">
              Because when women lead, everyone rises.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
              Educator. Entrepreneur. Sojourner. Storyteller. Kristi Hemmer is on a mission to put
              more women in power—because when women lead, the world is a better place for all of us.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <div class="relative">
              <img
                src="/images/KristiAge8-2000.jpg"
                alt="8-year-old Kristi Hemmer"
                class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full"
              />
              <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-sunny-yellow text-charcoal px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <p class="font-bold">Age 8: "I want to be President"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: Kristi's Story -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <div class="mb-20 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
              The Journey from <span class="text-moxie-pink">Classroom</span> to <span class="text-sunny-yellow">Global Changemaker</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-2xl text-gray-700 italic max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              "I want more women in power because when women lead, the world is a safer and more equitable place for everyone."
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Story Content -->
          <div class="space-y-12 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

            <!-- Dream Block -->
            <div class="bg-sunny-yellow bg-opacity-20 p-10 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-sunny-yellow mb-12">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-charcoal">It Started with a Dream</h3>
              <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
                At 8 years old, Kristi declared she wanted to be President of the United States.
                Bold. Unapologetic. Full of MOXIE. But somewhere along the way, like so many girls,
                she learned to shrink. To be polite. To be "good."
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Education Career -->
            <div class="mb-12">
              <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
                Fast forward to her career as an educator—spanning 20+ years from PreK through college,
                as a teacher, counselor, and principal. Kristi watched the same pattern repeat itself.
                Brilliant girls making themselves smaller. Talented women doubting their voices.
                Leaders hesitating to step into their power.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Turning Point Block -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center my-16">
              <img
                src="/images/kristi-header-1.png"
                alt="Kristi Hemmer speaking"
                class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full"
              />
              <div>
                <div class="bg-moxie-pink text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Turning Point</p>
                  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Kristi realized she couldn't keep watching this pattern. She quit her six-figure
                    job to dedicate herself to one mission: helping women reclaim their MOXIE and
                    step into power.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Global Journey -->
            <div class="mb-12">
              <p class="text-lg leading-loose mb-6">
                She didn't just read about women's empowerment—she went searching for it. Kristi has
                traveled to <strong class="text-moxie-pink">65 countries across all 7 continents</strong>,
                learning from women leaders, changemakers, and trailblazers around the globe.
              </p>

              <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
                From those experiences, she founded the <strong class="text-moxie-pink">Academy for Women's
                Empowerment (AWE)</strong>, a social enterprise connecting women across borders through
                education, leadership development, and global experiences.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Book Block -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo text-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-xl my-16">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Book That Started a Movement</h3>
              <p class="text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                In her book <em>"Quit Being So Good: Uncovering the Power of Breaking the Rules and
                Disappointing Everyone (Including Yourself)"</em>, Kristi challenges women to stop
                performing "goodness" and start claiming their power.
              </p>
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                The message is clear: Being unapologetic isn't selfish. It's necessary.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Today -->
            <div class="mb-12">
              <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
                Today, Kristi works as a speaker, coach, and facilitator—helping women leaders transform
                their courage, grit, and authenticity into lasting impact. She's a TEDx speaker, ICF
                certified coach, and advocate for the UN Sustainable Development Goals.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Final Quote -->
            <div class="text-center py-12 mt-16 border-t-2 border-moxie-pink border-opacity-30">
              <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-moxie-pink mb-6 leading-tight">
                "When women lead, the world is a safer and more equitable place for everyone."
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">This isn't just a tagline. It's a mission.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: Video Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Kristi in Action</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Watch Kristi share her vision for women's leadership and the power of MOXIE.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div id="video-container" class="relative aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl cursor-pointer group">
            <!-- Video Thumbnail - Using YouTube's thumbnail as fallback -->
            <img
              id="video-thumbnail"
              src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/ADyZp4tdHso/maxresdefault.jpg"
              alt="Kristi Hemmer - Unapologetic"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <!-- Play Button Overlay -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black bg-opacity-40 group-hover:bg-opacity-60 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-moxie-pink rounded-full p-6 group-hover:bg-sunny-yellow transition-colors duration-300 shadow-2xl">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path d="M6.3 2.841A1.5 1.5 0 004 4.11V15.89a1.5 1.5 0 002.3 1.269l9.344-5.89a1.5 1.5 0 000-2.538L6.3 2.84z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white text-xl font-bold mt-6 drop-shadow-lg">Watch Kristi's Story</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <script>
          document.getElementById('video-container')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
            const container = this;
            const iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
            iframe.setAttribute('src', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/ADyZp4tdHso?autoplay=1');
            iframe.setAttribute('title', 'Kristi Hemmer - Unapologetic');
            iframe.setAttribute('frameborder', '0');
            iframe.setAttribute('allow', 'accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture');
            iframe.setAttribute('allowfullscreen', '');
            iframe.className = 'w-full h-full';

            container.innerHTML = '';
            container.appendChild(iframe);
            container.classList.remove('cursor-pointer', 'group');
          });
        </script>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: Credentials & Expertise -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Credentials & Expertise</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <!-- Credential 1 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_01.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">M.Ed. Counseling</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Master's in Education & Counseling</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sunny-yellow to-yellow-400 text-charcoal p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Black_02.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">20+ Years</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Education: PreK-College</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 3 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-fierce-flamingo to-moxie-pink-alt text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_03.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Leadership Roles</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Teacher, Counselor, Principal</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 4 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-gray-700 text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Yellow_04.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">ICF Certified</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Professional Coach Certification</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 5 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_0.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">TEDx Speaker</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">International Keynote Speaker</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 6 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sunny-yellow to-yellow-400 text-charcoal p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Black_06.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Published Author</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">"Quit Being So Good"</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 7 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-fierce-flamingo to-moxie-pink-alt text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_02.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">65 Countries</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">All 7 Continents Traveled</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Credential 8 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-gray-700 text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
              <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Yellow_06.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Social Entrepreneur</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Founder of AWE</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5: Roles/Expertise Areas -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What Kristi Does</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Role 1: Author -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-white text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_04.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Author</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  Published author of "Quit Being So Good," challenging women to break free from
                  people-pleasing and claim their power.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Thousands of readers transformed</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Role 2: Speaker -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-sunny-yellow to-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-charcoal text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Black_01.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Speaker</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  TEDx and international keynote speaker inspiring audiences on women's leadership,
                  gender equity, and the power of MOXIE.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Organizations globally transformed</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Role 3: Social Entrepreneur -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-fierce-flamingo to-moxie-pink-alt flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-white text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_06.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Social Entrepreneur</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  Founder of AWE (Academy for Women's Empowerment), connecting women across borders
                  through education and leadership development.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Global network of changemakers</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Role 4: Coach -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-white text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Yellow_03.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Executive Coach</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  ICF certified coach helping women leaders amplify their impact through the PoWer
                  Course and individual coaching sessions.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Leaders transformed, voices amplified</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Role 5: Sojourner -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-white text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_White_02.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Sojourner</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  Global traveler to 65 countries and all 7 continents, facilitating PoWer Camp
                  retreats and immersive leadership experiences.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Cross-cultural connections forged</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Role 6: Mentor -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-sunny-yellow to-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-charcoal text-center p-6">
                  <img src="/images/Graphic Elements_Black_04.png" alt="" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Mentor</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  Auntie to many, mentor to changemakers, and guide for women stepping into
                  leadership with courage and authenticity.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-moxie-pink font-semibold">Impact: Next generation inspired</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 6: UN Global Goals & Mission -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Mission Statement -->
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">The MOXIE Mission</h2>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo text-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
                "To put more women in power—because when women lead, the world is a better place for all of us."
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl">
                This isn't just rhetoric. Research proves it. When women lead, communities thrive,
                economies grow, and equity expands.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- UN SDGs -->
          <div class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Aligned with UN Sustainable Development Goals</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              <!-- SDG 5 -->
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-moxie-pink to-fierce-flamingo text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Gender Equality</h4>
                <p class="text-lg">
                  Achieve gender equality and empower all women and girls through leadership,
                  education, and decision-making power.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- SDG 4 -->
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sunny-yellow to-yellow-400 text-charcoal p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
               
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Quality Education</h4>
                <p class="text-lg">
                  Ensure inclusive and equitable quality education and promote lifelong learning
                  opportunities for all.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- SDG 10 -->
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-gray-700 text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
               
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Reduced Inequalities</h4>
                <p class="text-lg">
                  Reduce inequality within and among countries through empowered voices and
                  equitable policies.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Research/Statistics -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Why Women's Leadership Matters</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-moxie-pink mb-2">↑21%</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Higher profitability in companies with gender-diverse leadership</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-moxie-pink mb-2">2x</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700">More likely to invest in education and community well-being</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-moxie-pink mb-2">↓40%</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Reduction in conflict when women are at negotiating tables</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-6">
              <a href="#" class="text-moxie-pink font-semibold hover:underline">
                Download One-Pager PDF →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 7: Values -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Core Values</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <!-- Value 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-moxie-pink">Interdependence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
                We rise together. Leadership isn't about individual achievement—it's about creating
                connections, building community, and lifting each other up.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-moxie-pink">MOXIE</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
                Courage. Grit. Guts. Pluck. The audacity to challenge systems, speak truth, and
                demand change—even when it's uncomfortable.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-moxie-pink">Authenticity</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
                Show up as you are. No performance. No perfection. Just real, honest, unapologetic
                leadership rooted in who you truly are.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-moxie-pink">Being Real</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
                Truth-telling over people-pleasing. Fact-checked insights over empty promises.
                Savvy strategy over reckless disruption. Real change requires real commitment.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 8: CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-moxie-pink via-moxie-pink-alt to-fierce-flamingo text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/Graphic Elements_Yellow_06.png"
        alt=""
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 opacity-30"
        aria-hidden="true"
      />

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Changemake Together?</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Let's transform your MOXIE into POWER. Choose how we'll work together.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- CTA 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white text-charcoal p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
